A vintage-style illustration of a determined hedgehog character sprinting up a jagged mountain made of stacked paper documents, with the mountain path showing dramatic vertical cliff faces rising unexpectedly between sections. The hedgehog leaves a trail of completed checkmarks behind it while more loose papers flutter down from above, adding to the peak. The color palette features warm sepia tones, aged cream paper textures, and bold red accents on the steepest vertical sections. The composition shows the winding progress path from bottom-left toward a distant finish flag at the summit, with the overall feeling of an old adventure map or antique technical diagram with decorative borders and crosshatching shading techniques.
